{"id":46,"parent_id":30,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":46,"title":"2 Nephi 16","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],[".studySummary",["i","Isaiah sees the Lord—Isaiah’s sins are forgiven—He is called to prophesy—He prophesies of the rejection by the Jews of Christ’s teachings—A remnant will return—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/6"},"Isaiah 6"],". About 559–545",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.1","order":"05.13.016.5032"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"In"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"year"],"that king Uzziah died, I",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"saw"],"also the Lord sitting upon a throne, high and lifted up, and his train filled the temple."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.2","order":"05.13.016.5033"},["b","2"],"Above it stood the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"seraphim"],"; each one had six wings; with twain he covered his face, and with twain he covered his feet, and with twain he did fly."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.3","order":"05.13.016.5034"},["b","3"],"And one cried unto another, and said: Holy, holy, holy, is the Lord of Hosts; the whole earth is full of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"glory"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.4","order":"05.13.016.5035"},["b","4"],"And the posts of the door moved at the voice of him that cried, and the house was filled with smoke."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.5","order":"05.13.016.5036"},["b","5"],"Then said I: Wo is unto me! for I am undone; because I am a man of unclean lips; and I dwell in the midst of a people of unclean lips; for mine eyes have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"seen"],"the King, the Lord of Hosts."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.6","order":"05.13.016.5037"},["b","6"],"Then flew one of the seraphim unto me, having a live coal in his hand, which he had taken with the tongs from off the altar;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.7","order":"05.13.016.5038"},["b","7"],"And he laid it upon my mouth, and said: Lo, this has touched thy lips; and thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"iniquity"],"is taken away, and thy sin purged."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.8","order":"05.13.016.5039"},["b","8"],"Also I heard the voice of the Lord, saying:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Whom"],"shall I send, and who will go for us? Then I said: Here am I; send me."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.9","order":"05.13.016.5040"},["b","9"],"And he said: Go and tell this people—Hear ye indeed, but they understood not; and see ye indeed, but they perceived not."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.10","order":"05.13.016.5041"},["b","10"],"Make the heart of this people fat, and make their ears heavy, and shut their eyes—lest they see with their eyes, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"hear"],"with their ears, and understand with their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"heart"],", and be converted and be healed."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.11","order":"05.13.016.5042"},["b","11"],"Then said I: Lord, how long? And he said: Until the cities be wasted without inhabitant, and the houses without man, and the land be utterly desolate;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.12","order":"05.13.016.5043"},["b","12"],"And the Lord have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"removed"],"men far away, for there shall be a great forsaking in the midst of the land."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.13","order":"05.13.016.5044"},["b","13"],"But yet there shall be a tenth, and they shall return, and shall be eaten, as a teil tree, and as an oak whose substance is in them when they cast their leaves; so the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"holy seed"],"shall be the substance thereof."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.1a","order":"05.13.016.5045"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/6.1.1-13"},"Isa. 6:1 (1–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.1b","order":"05.13.016.5047"},["b","1b"],["span.small","IE"],"about 750",["span.small","B.C."]],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.1c","order":"05.13.016.5049"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.41"},"John 12:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/11.2"},"2 Ne. 11:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.2a","order":"05.13.016.5051"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/seraphim"},"BD Seraphim"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.3a","order":"05.13.016.5053"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/72.19.19-20"},"Ps. 72:19 (19–20)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-glory-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Glory of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.5a","order":"05.13.016.5055"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-antemortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Antemortal"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.7a","order":"05.13.016.5057"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cleanse"},"TG Cleanse"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.8a","order":"05.13.016.5059"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.10a","order":"05.13.016.5061"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.14.14-15"},"Matt. 13:14 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.40"},"John 12:40"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/28.26-27"},"Acts 28:26–27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.8"},"Rom. 11:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.10b","order":"05.13.016.5063"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/2.2"},"Prov. 2:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.12a","order":"05.13.016.5065"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/17.18.18,20"},"2 Kgs. 17:18 (18, 20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/25.21"},"25:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/16.13a","order":"05.13.016.5067"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/9.2"},"Ezra 9:2"],"."]]}
